44
00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:18.770
Apakah itu?

45
00:03:18.770 --> 00:03:22.940
Maki -kun bilang dia tidak suka kelompok besar,

46
00:03:20.990 --> 00:03:22.730
Persetan?

47
00:03:22.730 --> 00:03:24.720
